CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 14, 1958, pg. B6, reads: "COLLEGE GRADUATE Lillian Warron, of 3408 Iowa St., smiles before receiving her Bachelor of Arts Degree"
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Lillian Warron wearing dark cap and gown, after receiving Bachelor of Arts Degree, at University of Pittsburgh graduation
